{"word":"θυμός","slug":"θυμός","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ϑυμός, οῦ, ὁ</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:θύω\">θύω</a></el>] ‘passionate state of mind’, the precise quality determined by context<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp> intense desire, passion <a href='B:730 14:8'>Rv 14:8</a></b> and <b>18:3,</b> with <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ prob.\">prob.</a> overlapping of the idea in<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp> wrath, anger <a href='B:510 19:28'>Ac 19:28</a>; <a href='B:520 2:8'>Ro 2:8</a>; <a href='B:540 12:20'>2 Cor 12:20</a>; <a href='B:560 4:31'>Eph 4:31</a>; <a href='B:650 11:27'>Hb 11:27</a>; <a href='B:730 12:12'>Rv 12:12</a>; <a href='B:730 14:10'>14:10</a>,</b> and <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ freq.\">freq.</a> in Rv of God’s <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ὀργή\">ὀργή</a></el>. <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:θυμομαχέω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:θυμόω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}